  keywords = {image segmentation;image colour analysis;hierarchical approach;color image segmentation;uniform regions;multilevel thresholding;homogeneity histogram;peak-finding algorithm;histogram analysis;color feature hue;unstable points;hue values;hierarchical segmentation;region merging process;over-segmentation;CIE(L*a*b*) color space;color images;Image segmentation;Histograms;Image color analysis;Merging;Image edge detection;Two dimensional displays;Sun;Infrared detectors;Performance analysis;Extraterrestrial measurements}
